timeline.bodyText:
Hm, this should remove any annotation on a class that is annotated with a scope. Is that intentional? If so, then this could be replaced with something like:
if (scopes.isScopeIn(ctx.getAnnotations())) {
  ctx.transform().removeAll().done();
}

